fields.title: Some Truth
fields.info: The depicted persons are the siblings Lucy and Linus van Pelt. They are sitting in school, Lucy is writing, supposedly engaging in a task given by the teacher. While Linus sits in front of an opened book, seemingly adhering to his assignment, he is giving a remark about school education, questioning the purpose of it in general.
